pageProduct.description:
General Information

  • Special natural face formula, rich of beech buds and bio-technologic originated hyaluronic acid, which respects sensitive skin, yet fights cutaneous ageing.
  • Formulated with an allergen free fragrance and emulsifiers derived from Olive Oil. 
  • Helps hypersensitive skin rebuild the epidermic protective barrier and to regain its own natural balance.
  • Colorants, alcohol and soap free.
